1610168765_1QHTwjj9nMpqDE1yb9t9ri6HSCt9M.body:
> [deuxzaron](#comment_35_1M1U9ZvF9XJmt4oPY4TLBWHJZWDdRpXFFy): I know the answer to this so it's mostly rhetorical but.Why do they need AWS anyways? Where is the competition to AWS?

AWS powers the service. Parler is centralized, so no hardware in the background means no communication. Amazon's comparable competition (Google and Microsoft) will similarly get pulled down. And I don't know if the userbase is ready and willing to pay to shitpost.
